# Task 1: Website UI Redesign

## Objective

Analyze an existing website and redesign its interface to improve clarity, structure, usability, and visual appeal.

## Problems Identified

* Cluttered layout
* Poor navigation
* Weak color scheme
* Lack of visual hierarchy
* Poor readability

## UI Principles Applied

* Visual Hierarchy
* Consistency
* Alignment
* White Space
* Accessibility

## Improvements Made

* Simplified navigation menu
* Modern color palette
* Better typography
* Improved spacing
* Organized content using sections and cards

